node.text: “How precious to me are your thoughts, God. How vast is the sum of them! Were I to count them, they would outnumber the grains of sand—when I awake, I am still with you.” -Psalm 139:17-18

node.text:
On the second day of EF, shop 25% OFF ALL RINGS! 🤩 Use 'BIRTHDAYWEEK' at checkout to redeem ✨⠀
⠀
Fun fact: In 2016, we were shipping all of our packages out of our founder's parent's living room!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 10, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and jewelry.

node.text:
Our birthday is coming up, and we’re celebrating big this year with a look back at our journey! 🎉

Check in daily to find out the sale of the day and fun facts about each year we’ve been around!

In 2015, our story began with a handful of bracelets and a dream. We were founded in Wisconsin back in August of 2015, launching with around 20 stone bracelets.

Last chance to shop 25% off ALL Bracelets today until our next discounted collection tomorrow! ✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Let go of your concerns tonight and give them to God, He's got you 💙

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Elevated Faith on August 08, 2021 tagging @jazzy_fizzlee3. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: The Lord is near, do not fear 💙 our prayer tonight is that you do not fear whatever the week ahead will bring, but that you choose to trust in Him instead. God loves you, and He's there for you tonight.
